  "changenote" "v2.7.1 — Spawn Stalling Fix + Mini-Horde Spam Fix\n\n• FIX: Zombies no longer stop spawning mid-siege during cooldown phases\n  - Baseline tide now draws from total budget continuously (no more exhausting early)\n  - Cooldowns scale with zombie count — small sieges get short cooldowns, big sieges fill the night\n\n• FIX: Mini-hordes no longer trigger endlessly\n  - MaxPerDay=0 now correctly means ZERO hordes per day (was accidentally unlimited)\n  - Kill heat from mini-horde fights no longer feeds the next trigger\n  - Generator heat reduced (15 to 8) to prevent generator-adjacent bases from constant triggers\n\n• Siege duration auto-scales with PZ day length setting (2-hour days = proportionally longer sieges)\n• Solo play overhauled — zombies path properly in singleplayer\n• CorpseSanity disabled in solo (prevented false-positive zombie kills)\n• Custom sounds disabled (no sound assets shipped yet)\n• Mini-hordes disabled by default"
}
